1. *Misija* mu je bila da očisti ulice od zločina. (His mission was to clean the streets of crime.)
2. Učesnici takmičenja su imali zadatak da ispunjavaju *misije*. (The participants of the competition had the task of completing missions.)
3. On je dobio *misiju* da promeni svet. (He was given the mission to change the world.)
4. Ona je služila svoju *misiju* do kraja. (She served her mission until the end.)
5. Oni su uspeli da ispunjavaju svoju *misiju*. (They managed to fulfill their mission.)